name: In The Middle of Nowhere
description:
In The Middle of Nowhere is the 1st artwork for the Out of Nowhere Series.

This 3d animation tries to illustrate how wealth, prosperity, and abundance that we could get in the middle of nowhere.

The symbol on the flag is Xun (巽). Xun/Wind is one of the Eight Trigrams. In the eight-trigram system, it symbolizes the wind. The wind blows and disperses gently and permeates everything.


3D Animation 1080 x 1080 px
